      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月のテンペストがデビューしてしばらく経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Shortly after Moon Tempest’s debut",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.8333333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ふーむ……悩ましいですわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*Hmm* That’s troubling…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "気高さと可憐さは超一級\n歩く姿は百合の花と名高い私とはいえ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Troubling even for me‚ one of superlative nobility and cuteness‚\nand resembling a lily in my walking deportment…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "こればかりは解決の糸口が見えませんわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In just this matter I can’t see any clue to a solution…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "自画自賛しながら何を悩んでるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something’s bothering you as you sing your own praises?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "あら、{user}さん\n聞いていたんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}-san.\nYou were listening?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "聞いてたんじゃなくて、勝手に聞こえてきたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wasn’t listening‚ but I happened to overhear.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなのどっちでもいいですわ\n……そんなことより",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t care either way.\nMore to the point…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
